WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.446
Outcomes vary substantially by phenotype.

00:00:02.446 --> 00:00:05.870
Approximately half of acute lymphocytic cases recover

00:00:05.870 --> 00:00:09.295
fully, but one in five progresses to

00:00:09.295 --> 00:00:10.273
dilated cardiomyopathy.

00:00:10.273 --> 00:00:13.697
Nearly ten percent require cardiac transplantation, and

00:00:13.697 --> 00:00:17.122
fulminant or giant-cell disease carries mortality exceeding

00:00:17.122 --> 00:00:18.100
forty percent.
